   <strong><a href="./RavenRed">RavenRed</a></strong>: In relation to ToME, yes! Let's face it, Tolkien was an apalling coder. <img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/smile4.png" alt=";-)" height="15" width="15"> (Though, to give him his due, he did invent his own language) This is getting extremely silly, I'm stopping now...  
